{
  "2330930": {
    "name": "夜行之旅：放置式角色扮演冒险",
    "steam_appid": 2330930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330930/extras/7cb83ec578204b8567196997b2ac183b.avif?t=1769978692\" width=1513 height=355 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《夜行之旅》是一款半放置式RPG游戏。玩家可以招募英雄、击败怪物、打造武器与护甲、强化天赋树、为装备附魔与重铸、发现神秘宝石，最终组建出最强大的冒险小队！ <br> <br><strong>请注意：放置玩法是本作的核心组成部分之一。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款半放置游戏，同时拥有深度且复杂的装备词条系统，支持近乎无限的角色流派构筑！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多可选择6种冒险者职业。每个职业拥有2种专精，每种专精包含3个技能。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制 + 实时机制战斗系统：战斗中，每个单位根据“先攻”属性依次行动；但触发效果、增益/减益持续效果以及生命恢复等则以“实时”方式运作。这一独特系统带来更深层次的战术策略。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过100种主动与被动技能可供尝试与搭配。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >附魔、重铸与属性转移系统，让冒险者的装备拥有极高自定义空间。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度宝石系统与多种套装加成，进一步扩展你的策略选择。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过20种怪物类型，分布在6张不同地图中。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吸引居民、派遣探索队，不断扩建和发展你的城镇！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br>打造独特流派，投入战斗！ </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330930/extras/dd38d6e3c555d32f76e07d281e6a37da.poster.avif?t=1769978692\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330930/extras/dd38d6e3c555d32f76e07d281e6a37da.webm?t=1769978692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330930/extras/dd38d6e3c555d32f76e07d281e6a37da.mp4?t=1769978692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在植物学家处培育魔法果实！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330930/extras/7f89846476be50e6f5dad42802a936c1.avif?t=1769978692\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330930/extras_big/7f89846476be50e6f5dad42802a936c1.webp?t=1769978692 width=1560 height=874 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在炼金术士处调制魔法药剂！</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330930/extras/30588a22d6430a1a00720b57edf4b51b.avif?t=1769978692\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330930/extras_big/30588a22d6430a1a00720b57edf4b51b.webp?t=1769978692 width=1560 height=910 /></span></h2>",
